        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>Full-Stack Web Developer</h2>
          <p>
            I'm equipped with a drive to create innovative and User-friendly
            digital experiences. With a strong foundation in professional
            practices both in front-end and back-end development.
            <br />
            My expertise spans a range of best performing technologies and
            frameworks, including<span class="tech-decor">
              HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node.js, MongoDB...</span
            >
            I'm always eager to learn and adapt to new technologies, ensuring my
            skills stay up-to-date and relevant.
          </p>
          <p>
            As a full-stack developer, I enjoy the challenge of bringing ideas
            to life, from conceptualization to deployment. My goal is to craft
            seamless, intuitive and visually stunning experiences that leave a
            lasting impression.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not coding, you can either find me enjoying nice moments
            with my family or surfing the internet. I'm excited to collaborate
            with like-minded individuals and contribute my skills to build
            something amazing.
          </p>
          <p>
            Feel free to explore my portfolio and get in touch for discussion on
            opportunities and projects.
          </p>
          <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; position: relative">
            <a href="#contact" class="about-btn">Get in Touch!</a
            ><span class="point-icon">👈🏽</span>
          </div>
        </div>
